## 5. AnnouncementController.java — complete

**File:** `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-server/src/main/java/com/yottastudios/ns/collabspace/announcement/controller/AnnouncementController.java`

Endpoints:
| Annotation | Path | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `@PostResource` | `/announcement/create` | POST | Create/update announcement |
| `@GetResource` | `/announcement/list/waiting` | GET | List waiting announcements |
| `@GetResource` | `/announcement/list/published` | GET | List published + mark first as read |
| `@PostResource` | `/announcement/update` | POST | Change status/type |
